name: Membership status
query:
SELECT 
    full_name as 'Name',
    membership_plan as 'Membership plan', 
    membership_status as 'Membership status', 
    payment_status as 'Payment status', 
    start_date as 'Start date', 
    end_date as 'End date', 
    amount_paid as 'Amount paid', 
    outstanding_amount as 'Outstanding Amount'
FROM tabMembers;
